com.netflix.governator.guice

Class ModuleListBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.netflix.governator.guice.ModuleListBuilder

  • public class ModuleListBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    The ModuleListBuilder keeps track of modules and their transitive dependencies and provides a mechanism to replace or exclude modules. When build() is called a list of modules is created and modules will be ordered in the order in which they were added while allowing for dependent modules to be listed first.
